 God Neptune didnt appreciate the sarcasim. As the stopped about 20 feet from 
the signal he lowered himself 5 feet from the ground and dropped her on her 
but. He landed and turned to Galvatron. " I have a net we can use. We just 
have to get her still in one place. I sense many bot signatures on the other 
side of her. That may give us time." Galvatron thought about this. "That is 
not enough insurance. Dark Mouse could you put her down or at least slow her 
down enough for us to grab her?"

--part1_3a.19979a47.28b69609_boundary
